    "key": "06aea011-a083-4ee7-a175-46a27ca8eade",
    "name": "Overview",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Overview",
    "content": "<p>Prior to joining academia, Ramchandra practiced accountancy in the public sector. He is a Chartered Global Management Accountant (CGMA) and a Fellow with AdvanceHE.</p>\n<p>Ramchandra has extensive involvement and a keen interest in quality assurance and enhancement of higher education provisions in national and transnational settings.</p>\n<p>He regularly participates in and contributes to the validation, revalidation, and accreditation of HE courses.</p>\n<p><span class=\"lead\">Affiliations and Memberships:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Chartered Institute of Management Accountants (CIMA)</li>\n<li>British Accounting and Finance Association (BAFA) - Executive Board</li>\n<li>Member - BAFA Scotland</li>\n<li>British-Nepal Academic Council</li>\n</ul>"
  },
  {
    "key": "7eefb089-9072-4591-a101-dae91356a3a6",
    "name": "Research Interests",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Research Interests ",
    "content": "<p><span class=\"lead\">Research Overview:</span></p>\n<p>Ramchandra's core research interests include sustainable financing (particularly for small and medium-sized enterprises - SMEs), fintech and access to finance, and sustainability accounting.</p>\n<p><span class=\"lead\"><strong>Active research interests: </strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Sustainable Finance</li>\n<li>Environmental, Social, and Governance (ESG) considerations in financing and investment decision-making and reporting</li>\n<li>Access to finance for SMEs and Fintech and financial inclusion</li>\n<li>Accounting for sustainability</li>\n</ul>\n<p> <span class=\"lead\"><strong>Research Methods</strong>:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Questionnaires and interviews</li>\n<li>Econometrics and time series analysis</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"lead\">Research Centre Membership:</span></p>\n<p>Associate Member of <a href=\"/{localLink:umb://document/9e59330129ac41028d861633fdcb6a2d}\" title=\"Centre for Applied Social Sciences\">Centre for Applied Social Sciences</a></p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "cfb0db62-fa19-40b4-85dd-8cb2b3143f2f",
    "name": "Teaching & Learning",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Teaching & Learning",
    "content": "<p>Ramchandra teaches a number of finance and accounting-related modules to both undergraduate and postgraduate courses.</p>\n<p>He serves as a committee member for the school academic board, the senate of the university, and the convener of the undergraduate programme committee.</p>\n<p>Ramchandra supervises UG, PG, and PhD theses in finance and accounting areas.</p>"
  }
]]]></Value>
